data.description: Unique log cabin with peek-a-boo lake views in Clearwood. This home has an open and airy floorplan with plenty of room to spread out. Upper floor is open and looks out to the lake while featuring 2 bedrooms, a sitting area and a bonus/office space. Downstairs the open kitchen hosts SS appliances, quartz countertops, vinyl plank flooring, built in hand sanitizer and water spout for cooking. A separate dining room, living area, rec room and large wall of windows complete the main area. Head downstairs to find a fully finished basement with 2 entrances that can easily be converted to a large family room. Roof less then 3 years old. Enjoy all amenities including 3 lakes, trails, playgrounds, seasonal pool and tennis courts.
